<item>
            <title>[PIG-2997] Provide a convenience constructor on PigServer that accepts Configuration</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2997</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;PigServer currently has Properties based constructor. Hadoop in general deals with Configuration and it would be good to have a PigServer constructor that accepts the same. With this, user does not have to worry about creating Properties object out of conf and can simply invoke this new constructor.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
